Contents of this README
-----------------------

1. How to compile RawIVEditor
2. How to run RawIVEditor
3. How to use RawIVEditor

*********************************************************

1. How to compile RawIVEditor

Uses Trolltech's qmake. Volume Rover is compatible with QT 3.0.*

- QT 3.0.+ needs to be installed

Type:

qmake; make

*********************************************************

2. How to run RawIVEditor

Run 
./RawIVEditor

Data types that the RawIV Editor can view:
	- rawiv. A description of the rawiv file format is here:
	http://www.ticam.utexas.edu/~shrew/formats/

*********************************************************

3. How to use RawIVEditor

When run, a file window will appear.  To modify the header
of a RawIV file, select the file in the file window and
press ok.  To create a new RawIV header, press cancel.
Make any changes the the fields of the header, then press
ok to save the header.